author: guitargeek
body:
#### PR description:

This is one of the occasional PRs that removes old electron IDs as the goal is still to have only the VIDs and other currently used IDs left in the release. This time, I remove the old Likelihood based IDs and some old cut based IDs. One working point is still used in PF, so I move it there.

@Sam-Harper

#### PR validation:

CMSSW compiles and local matrix tests pass.

#### if this PR is a backport please specify the original PR:

No backport intended.
title: RecoEgamma/ElectronIdentification cleanup
